mobile<br />\n<br />\nosmo mobile就防水同有motion timeslape...缺點唔知邊度買到support go pro既配件,就算有係咪support番手柄？<br />\n<br />\nFreeVision ViltaG就無防水同無motion timeslape...但apps強大同輕過osmo,又可以用到osmo d 配件..所以唔知點擇"},{"pid":"daaa2c6507dca8095bf0fd23fdfb27ba3a73c777","tid":504421,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T07:31:36.000Z","msg":"In DJI, I TRUST!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66853875d113e48f305e60fa0abfde22ee7f38cd","tid":504421,"uid":43483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T07:33:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/21/153315_f41d973d40b58962f2bdbf08c106142d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F21%2F153315_f41d973d40b58962f2bdbf08c106142d.jpg&h=41e61e50&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dc220cf9363e1dd553308a786889680ccc55b50","tid":504421,"uid":2331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T12:06:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>考慮緊FreeVision ViltaG同osmo mobile<br />\n<br />\nosmo mobile就防水同有motion timeslape...缺點唔知邊度買到support go pro既配件,就算有係咪support番手柄？<br />\n<br />\nFreeVision ViltaG就無防水同無motion timeslape...但apps強大同輕過osmo,又可以用到osmo d 配件..所以唔知點擇</blockquote><br />\nOsmo mobile防水？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6541aa24927864a52ca984afd45ce77e02813e81","tid":504421,"uid":103228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T12:30:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>考慮緊FreeVision ViltaG同osmo mobile<br />\n<br />\nosmo mobile就防水同有motion timeslape...缺點唔知邊度買到support go pro既配件,就算有係咪support番手柄？<br />\n<br />\nFreeVision ViltaG就無防水同無motion timeslape...但apps強大同輕過osmo,又可以用到osmo d 配件..所以唔知點擇</blockquote><br />\nOsmo mobile防水？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔防架？<br />\n咁我可能記錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f655b120b4a86f6803f702fd2fdc4370a3fdd7c","tid":504421,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T15:29:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 買返gopro原廠個支<br />\n其他去外國凍少少都收皮、入水又易壞、夾gopro又唔穩陣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原廠 karma grip有兩個嚴重問題：<br />\n1. 無方向制，要扭動支掍轉向，係一個白痴設計<br />\n2. Gopro沒電了換電池就好,而Grip不能停止供電到Gopro，用耐了gopro 滿電的girp卻沒電了而充電很慢</blockquote><br />\n運動鏡頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跳緊傘、滑緊雪仲得閒用方向制？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你想連續運動幾多個鐘？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話就話唔防水，個人用落，落雨、落雪都唔會話用唔到，應該有專登計設過<br />\n其他支那野凍少少就收鳩皮、配gopro又唔用原廠個gopro夾設計，用黎拍運動都驚甩出黎<br />\n<br />\n當然，如你用黎拍普通片，建議你用返手機配穩定器算，gopro個廣角鏡用黎拍普通片真係好7"},{"pid":"e3c6a3f47d6de0c5c6696315758f84b55d51548f","tid":504421,"uid":49594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T01:23:56.000Z","msg":"如果你唔怕世俗眼光<br />\n你可以將go pro 綁係雞頭<br />\n抱住隻雞來拍攝"},{"pid":"d3b044230e29e5a1b5e35191a13a45dd1d9d1ae2","tid":504421,"uid":103228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T01:39:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果你唔怕世俗眼光<br />\n你可以將go pro 綁係雞頭<br />\n抱住隻雞來拍攝</blockquote><br />\n店晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3674ec2dd9fd716cb425ebead1a44bab0e992983","tid":504421,"uid":103228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T01:40:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 買返gopro原廠個支<br />\n其他去外國凍少少都收皮、入水又易壞、夾gopro又唔穩陣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原廠 karma grip有兩個嚴重問題：<br />\n1. 無方向制，要扭動支掍轉向，係一個白痴設計<br />\n2. Gopro沒電了換電池就好,而Grip不能停止供電到Gopro，用耐了gopro 滿電的girp卻沒電了而充電很慢</blockquote><br />\n運動鏡頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跳緊傘、滑緊雪仲得閒用方向制？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你想連續運動幾多個鐘？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話就話唔防水，個人用落，落雨、落雪都唔會話用唔到，應該有專登計設過<br />\n其他支那野凍少少就收鳩皮、配gopro又唔用原廠個gopro夾設計，用黎拍運動都驚甩出黎<br />\n<br />\n當然，如你用黎拍普通片，建議你用返手機配穩定器算，gopro個廣角鏡用黎拍普通片真係好7</blockquote><br />\n有時我要吸係架車出面拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我諗住買freevision個隻又有得拆個雲台出黎&hellip;配相機件又得&hellip;osom件又得。"},{"pid":"1814351aef7c1ff579b8b28c5b8b7f88306cdc09","tid":504421,"uid":130225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T03:06:18.000Z","msg":"支持香港牌子... Swiftcam M4!"},{"pid":"914bfeee5fa770e82af5b938ccddf9b3bcea6e65","tid":504421,"uid":33562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T14:15:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>smooth q</blockquote><br />\n準係for到電話？</blockquote><br />\n可以加配件夾gopro<br />\n利申用緊"},{"pid":"ab1752ae990d3da6c576595edb8c64f23bffc5d7","tid":504421,"uid":142203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"914bfeee5fa770e82af5b938ccddf9b3bcea6e65","tid":504421,"uid":33562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T14:15:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>smooth q</blockquote><br />\n準係for到電話？</blockquote><br />\n可以加配件夾gopro<br />\n利申用緊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T17:35:36.000Z","msg":"咩配件?"},{"pid":"cd5ad5db8bc0c8dc5181d9b963ae09c96c3eef0c","tid":504421,"uid":33562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab1752ae990d3da6c576595edb8c64f23bffc5d7","tid":504421,"uid":142203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"914bfeee5fa770e82af5b938ccddf9b3bcea6e65","tid":504421,"uid":33562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T14:15:43.000Z","m